258
00:21:27,700 --> 00:21:29,200
Brat Hao! Ako to, že si tu?

259
00:21:29,300 --> 00:21:31,250
Rýchlo! Poď so mnou na pódium!

260
00:21:31,250 --> 00:21:32,750
Xiao Xiao! Xiao Xiao, pomôž mi!

261
00:21:32,750 --> 00:21:35,600
