- Rýchlo! Poď!

262
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:37,450
Rýchlo!

263
00:21:37,450 --> 00:21:38,150
Je koniec.

264
00:21:42,100 --> 00:21:42,800
No tak.

265
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:49,700
Čo teraz? Lu Hong Jian všetko zničí.

266
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,300
To nie je Lu Hong Jian!

267
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:10,800
Šéf je na pódiu!

268
00:22:11,850 --> 00:22:12,730
Šéf!

269
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,700
Milujem ťa!

270
00:22:18,730 --> 00:22:20,150
Brat Hao?

271
00:22:33,800 --> 00:22:36,150
Haló? Sestra Ling, rýchlo príď.

272
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:38,730
Má to poriadny úspech.

273
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:49,470
Sestra Ling, práve som...

274
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:50,850
videla brata Haa.

275
00:22:52,150 --> 00:22:54,690
Som zmätená, sestra Ling.

276
00:23:22,850 --> 00:23:33,270
Ešte! Ešte!

277
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:40,750
Haló, Šéf? Čo hovoríš, nepočujem ťa.

278
00:23:43,300 --> 00:23:44,590
Šéf, o čo ide?

279
00:23:46,500 --> 00:23:48,100
Čo sa to teraz stalo, Šéf?

